## Quick Reference

| Aspect | Pattern |
|--------|---------|
| **Queries** | `findBy*` (async, always) |
| **Expectations** | `await expect()` |
| **Custom events** | `addEventListener('eventName', handler)` |
| **Slots** | Query slotted content in light DOM |
| **Shadow DOM** | Use ARIA roles or `shadowRoot` direct access |
| **Boolean props** | `?prop` in lit, `toBeDisabled()` in assertions |
| **Object props** | `.prop` syntax in lit templates |
| **Timing** | `findBy*` handles waiting; avoid `setTimeout` |

---

## Checklist for Web Component Tests

✅ All queries use `findBy*` (async)
✅ All expectations use `await expect()`
✅ Custom events tested via `addEventListener` (not `fn()`)
✅ Slotted content verified in light DOM
✅ Shadow DOM elements accessed via ARIA roles when possible
✅ Boolean attributes use `?` prefix in lit templates
✅ Complex props use `.` prefix in lit templates
✅ No hard-coded timeouts (`setTimeout`)

